title: UQ Holder!: Mahou Sensei Negima! 2 (UQ Holder!)
synopsis: Touta Konoe is an ordinary boy raised in a small rural town. His mundane life suddenly changes when his mentor, Katherine McDowell, reveals herself to be a vampire; after saving Touta from a mortal wound, she causes him to become immortal as well.
